Depending of what you want to get off, next time I
would suggest Goof-Off. You can find in the paint dept
of you local Lowe's of Home Despot. Goo Gone is good
stuff, but it's a little sissy compared to Goof-Off.

That stuff is an awesome remover - just be careful
with it.

